c: 4
v: 95
t: "Ur aâdilen ara wid iqqimen si lmumnin, siwa wid ivôuôan, akked wid ijuhden deg ubrid n Öebbi, s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen. Ismenyaf Öebbi wid ijuhden s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen, i wid iqqimen. Akw, Iwaââed asen Öebbi ûûam. Ifrez Öebbi imjuhad af wid iqqimen, s warraz ameqwôaêan"